"-----------------Visuals----------------"
"Graphical vim uses the full atom-dark colorscheme
"instead of the 256 color version
colorscheme atom-dark

"-----------------Font-------------------"
"Set font type and font size.
set guifont=Fira\ Code\ 15
"Line-height.
set linespace=15

"-----------------Window-----------------"
"Hide the left and right scrollbars on windows and splits
set guioptions-=l
set guioptions-=L
set guioptions-=r
set guioptions-=R
